data.description: This Town Lakes Property, A Gated Community, with a Security Gate, and sidewalks and street lights. Town Lakes is fully developed. Some features are: Eat-in-Kitchen plus a dining/living open area for your family entertainment, Screeend  Lanai under truss in the rear with a scenic view of the preserve, Split Bedrooms for privacy . Primary bedroom with privacy Bathroom, Appliances to be Provided.  Its location is within easy access to grocery stores, doctors' offices, restaurants, and hospital. This Property is easily accessible to main highways to take you to beaches and more shops in Fort Myers and many other cities. Property is on city water and sewer. Note: Town Lakes is Professionally Managed. Come and see for yourself. Call for more info.
